action.description: Taken from Chief Clerk's desk.Placed on General File.Read third time. Amended. (Amend. No. 910.)Dispensed with reprinting.Read third time. Passed, as amended. Title approved, as amended. (Yeas: 39, Nays: None, Excused: 3.)To printer.From printer. To reengrossment. Reengrossed. Second reprint.To Senate.In Senate.Read first time. Referred to Committee on Finance. To committee.
